zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-0: 通过CTWing平台的HTTP推送服务进行数据接入
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-8: 1、CTWing端创建应用、产品、设备；配置完成后查看产品详情。其中产品ID以及Master-APIkey在JetLinks平台配置时会使用。
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-9: 2、IOT端创建类型为CTWing的设备接入网关
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-10: 3、IOT端创建产品，选中接入方式为CTWing，填写CTWing平台中的产品ID、Master-APIkey。
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-11: 4、IOT端添加设备，设备ID需要配置真实设备的IMEI号，配置完成后启用设备（如果启用设备提示错误，请检查CTWing网关参数是否配置正确）。
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-13: 真实设备的IMEI号，需要填写正确，否则推送数据会接收失败
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-17: 5、CTWing端配置产品/设备/分组级订阅，订阅方URL地址请填写：
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-18: （此处订阅地址可以在JetLinks平台中配置完成CTWing网关后再填写）。
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-19: 6、以上步骤配置完成后，可以触发真实设备进行上数，在平台对应设备详情页查看设备状态。
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-21: 在IOT端启用设备时，若CTWing平台没有与之对应的设备，则将在CTWing端自动创建新设备
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-22: 只能选择HTTP通信方式的协议
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-35: 2、创建产品，并选中接入方式为
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-36: CTWing,选中后需填写CTWing平台中的产品ID、Master-APIkey。
zh.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-37: 3、添加设备，为每一台设备设置唯一的IMEI、IMSI码（需与OneNet平台中填写的值一致，若OneNet平台没有对应的设备，将会通过OneNet平台提供的LWM2M协议自动创建）

en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-0: Accessing data through the HTTP push service on the CTVing platform
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-3: Up to 64 characters can be entered
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-8: 1. Create applications, products, and devices on the CTVing platform; View product details after configuration is complete. The product ID and Master API key will be used when configuring on the JetLinks platform.
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-9: 2. Create a device access gateway of CTWing type on the IOT end
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-10: 3. Create a product on the IOT end, select the access method as CTWing, and fill in the product ID and Master API key in the CTWing platform.
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-11: 4. To add a device on the IOT end, the device ID needs to be configured with the IMEI number of the real device. After configuration is complete, enable the device (if an error message appears when enabling the device, please check if the CTWing gateway parameters are configured correctly).
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-13: The IMEI number of the real device needs to be filled in correctly, otherwise the push data will fail to receive
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-14: The SN number of the real device
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-15: The IMSI number of the real device
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-16: PSK for real devices, not mandatory
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-17: 5. CTWing configuration product/device/group level subscription, please fill in the URL address of the subscriber:
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-18: (The subscription address here can be filled in after configuring the CTWing gateway on the JetLinks platform.).
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-19: 6. After completing the above steps of configuration, the real device can be triggered to count, and the device status can be viewed on the corresponding device detail page of the platform.
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-21: When enabling devices on the IOT end, if there is no corresponding device on the CTWing platform, a new device will be automatically created on the CTWing end
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-22: Only HTTP communication protocol can be selected
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-25: No data available at the moment

en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-35: 2. Create a product and select the access method as
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-36: CTWing, After selection, the product ID and Master API key from the CTWing platform need to be filled in.
en.Cloud.Ctwing.4282912-37: 3. Add devices and set unique IMEI and IMSI codes for each device (which must be consistent with the values filled in the OneNet platform.
